基本財務學
課程詳細內容


(H120200) 基本財務學


類別屬性

日間部 / 核心課程 / 必修 / 預計開課 


修業年級

大學部二年級 


資格限制



上課地點
會計系館 63104 


授課教師

王明隆


課程簡介
 This course will provide undergraduate students with a theoretical and practical framework in which financial decisions are analyzed.


授課大綱

1 Introduction, CF and Financial Statements Analysis 
2 Present Value, Future Value and Valuation of Securities 
3 Capital Budgeting: IRR and NPV 
4 Capital Investment Decisions and Project Risk Analysis 
5 Risk, Expected Return and Markowitz's Portfolio Theory 
6 CAPM, SML 
7 Cost of Capital and Capital Budgeting 
8 Efficient Market Hypothesis and Corporate Financing Decision 
9 Capital Structure 
10 Capital Budgeting for the Levered Firm 
11 Long-Term Financing, Stock and Bond 
12 Financial Planning and Short-Term Financing 
13 Option and Corporate Finance 
14 Warrants and Convertible 
15 Derivatives and Hedging Risk 
16 Review and Summary 







